         MACRO
&NAME    QTILT &MESSAGE
         USING QDISPLAY,R15   BASE REG FOR DISPLAY WORK AREA
&NAME    L     R15,QVDSPL     LOAD BASE REG
         MVC   QDHLINE,=CL80&MESSAGE
         MVC   QDMLNG,=H'0'   ZERO MESSAGE LENGTH
         DROP  R15
         L     R15,=V(DISPLAY) ADDR OF DISPLAY MODULE
         LR    R14,R15        SET FOR LOOP
         BR    R15            GO TO IT
         MEND
